### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health

### Test Database Connection
GET http://localhost:3000/api/test-db

### Sign Up
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "test123",
  "phone_number": "+1234567890"
}

### Sign In
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "test123"
}

### Add Memory (replace TOKEN with actual token from signup)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/memories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "title": "My First Memory",
  "description": "This is a wonderful memory from our trip",
  "memory_date": "2023-07-15",
  "location": "New York",
  "media_url": "https://example.com/image.jpg"
}

### Get Memories
GET http://localhost:3000/api/memories
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Add Journal
POST http://localhost:3000/api/journals
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "title": "Today's Thoughts",
  "content": "Today was a great day! I felt productive and happy.",
  "mood": "happy",
  "tags": ["productive", "reflection"]
}

### Add Reminder
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reminders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "title": "Doctor Appointment",
  "description": "Annual checkup with Dr. Smith",
  "reminder_date": "2025-11-20T10:00:00.000Z",
  "priority": "high"
}
